            <h2 class="sec-title text-title title-anime__title">Creative Learning</span></h2>
          </div>
          <p class="section-desc mb-4">
          
Engaging children, teachers, and parents for holistic development, our approach encourages students to explore, experiment, and express themselves. As a creativity-based and experiential learning school, we integrate hands-on activities into every subject, fostering problem-solving skills and a lasting love for learning.
          </p>
          
        <div class="title-area mb-4">
        
            <h2 class="sec-title text-title title-anime__title">Global Citizenship</span></h2>
          </div>
          <p class="section-desc mb-4">
          
We are committed to preparing students as responsible global citizens. As a global learning school in Mangalore, we promote understanding of diverse cultures, perspectives, and real-world challenges. Through collaborative and meaningful learning experiences, we empower students to contribute positively to an interconnected world.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right side: 2 Images -->
